text: Erest so landschere geth of exan up on erfdion þane up on conanleyghbrok þane up on thene wey þanen north on.
Wulwythelandschere at alfredes þane þare of dune to cridican.
Þanen up on grenewey on þar nedesslo þanen on dich of fulere.
Þane up on geganbrok of fonlangford þane on herepath of kingeslandschere.

Þane up rigt on bedesberghe of beddesberghe on bright hulle <Briggemores> <heved> <þanne> <a> <dun> <on> <streme> <on> <brigges> <mores> <biche> <midward> <þanne> <up> <rich> <overe> <drotarshulle> on blakanhulle.
Þanen a doun on lake so eft right on exan.
Þane a doun of exan of Kirfdian.
